17:23.999 --> 17:26.001
So anyway, hypothetically,

17:26.045 --> 17:28.003
you could get us out
of this jail cell.

17:28.047 --> 17:30.092
Uh-oh. TAYLOR:
No, it's all right.

17:30.136 --> 17:30.962
