30:42.014 --> 30:43.885
No, he made us hours ago.

30:43.929 --> 30:45.887
The info he gave you was a trap

30:45.931 --> 30:48.716
to send an SOS to Codex.
They're coming.

30:50.936 --> 30:53.721
All right, do we have
a black site ready?

30:53.764 --> 30:55.438
We need to transport
The Merchant out of here.

30:55.462 --> 30:57.657
Yeah, we're working on it,
butwe need a solid extraction plan

30:57.681 --> 30:59.007
in case we run into Codexon the way.

30:59.031 --> 30:59.988
Backup.
Why can't we call for backup?

31:00.032 --> 31:02.338
No.
Codex has infiltrated

31:02.382 --> 31:04.079
every level of
the government everywhere.

31:04.123 --> 31:05.230
We'd be calling in
reinforcements

31:05.254 --> 31:06.492
for them, not us. We're on our own.

31:06.516 --> 31:09.084
Oh, hello, Desiree.
Lovely to see you again.

31:09.128 --> 31:10.757
Don't you talk to her. She's lovely.
I can see why you're so devoted.

31:10.781 --> 31:12.740
Oh!

31:12.783 --> 31:13.959
Where's the Codex bunker?

31:14.002 --> 31:17.136
Tell me, or I swear to God... Calm down!

31:17.179 --> 31:19.094
Get off me.

31:19.138 --> 31:21.270
You are letting him
get to you. Calm down!

31:21.314 --> 31:22.619
I don't care. Get off me.

31:22.663 --> 31:23.707
Put him over there.

31:30.236 --> 31:33.195
Put chucklehead herein the war
room, with guards.

31:33.239 --> 31:34.980
Chucklehead? Really?

31:35.023 --> 31:36.416
You two. Ow!

31:36.459 --> 31:38.984
Make sure you lock
this building down

31:39.027 --> 31:40.507
while we come up with a plan.

31:45.120 --> 31:46.165
I'm good.

31:46.208 --> 31:47.644
I'm not.

31:51.779 --> 31:53.433
I'm sorry.

31:53.476 --> 31:55.130
It's been a rough
couple of days.

31:55.174 --> 31:57.021
I'm not allowed to lose my
cool every once in a while?

31:57.045 --> 31:59.830
Oh, you can. Just doesn't mean
it's not hard to watch.

31:59.874 --> 32:01.832
It's a part of an act.

32:01.876 --> 32:03.965
"Sacrifice the things you love."

32:04.009 --> 32:07.186
That's a confor The Merchant.

32:07.229 --> 32:09.318
Well, I believed you.

32:11.581 --> 32:14.628
I am losing my grip on which
version of you is real.

32:14.671 --> 32:17.936
The one who loves you is real.

32:22.114 --> 32:24.072
You can't just...

32:25.291 --> 32:27.554
We're in the middle...

32:30.339 --> 32:33.299
You love me?

32:36.128 --> 32:37.477
Well, cut it out.

32:37.520 --> 32:39.000
Ow.

32:39.044 --> 32:40.828
I'm sorry.

32:59.586 --> 33:01.544
Let's rendezvous
in the tech room

33:01.588 --> 33:03.131
after we lock the rest
of this place down.

33:03.155 --> 33:06.158
Hopefully, Matty has atransport
plan for The Merchant.

33:08.203 --> 33:10.205
Okay.

33:12.642 --> 33:15.167
Look at him,
he's just sittingin the war room,

33:15.210 --> 33:17.038
staring at us.

33:17.082 --> 33:20.041
I don't want to see his stupidface
any longer than I have to.

33:25.612 --> 33:27.005
We've got

33:27.048 --> 33:28.678
a black site in Tujungathat
