33:28.702 --> 33:32.445
All right, people,
this is goingto be Convoy Security 101.

33:32.488 --> 33:33.620
Motion on the roof.

33:33.663 --> 33:35.361
They're here.

33:36.405 --> 33:38.059
I recognize her.

33:38.103 --> 33:40.366
Last time we met, she was
pointing a shotgun at me.

33:40.409 --> 33:42.518
Looks like they're gonna work their way
down from the roof. TAYLOR: All right,

33:42.542 --> 33:44.022
everyone, take positions.

34:10.135 --> 34:12.528
Find The Merchant.

34:12.572 --> 34:14.574
I'll take her.

34:20.145 --> 34:21.711
You have no idea

34:21.755 --> 34:24.192
how badly I wanted
to punch somebody today.

34:30.242 --> 34:32.157
On your left! Move, move! Get down!

34:40.121 --> 34:41.601
Cover me! Covering you!

34:41.644 --> 34:43.429
Move around the corner!

34:43.472 --> 34:45.953
Grenade! MAN: Go, go, go!

34:47.650 --> 34:48.651
Get down!

34:56.790 --> 34:58.705
Let's go! Go!

35:39.006 --> 35:40.964
Shame.

35:44.316 --> 35:46.100
What's this?

35:50.104 --> 35:52.367
Titan wants you to call her.

35:52.411 --> 35:54.413
Right.

36:02.247 --> 36:03.726
Hel-Hello?

36:03.770 --> 36:05.293
You're welcome.

36:05.337 --> 36:06.816
Oh, thank you.

36:06.860 --> 36:10.385
Thank-thank you so, so much.
Thank you.

36:10.429 --> 36:11.647
What'd you tell them?

36:11.691 --> 36:12.971
Oh, I didn't tell them anything.

36:12.996 --> 36:14.276
Well, I didn't
tell them anything

36:14.302 --> 36:15.521
they didn't know already.

36:15.564 --> 36:17.305
And-and obviously,
anything I did say

36:17.349 --> 36:20.613
to hedge my loyalty
to Codex, well,

36:20.656 --> 36:23.224
th-that was an act.
But you know that.

36:23.268 --> 36:25.226
Good.

36:25.270 --> 36:27.228
Listen, I-I know

36:27.272 --> 36:28.510
that we've had our
differences in the past.

36:28.534 --> 36:30.144
I just wanted to thank you

36:30.188 --> 36:31.754
for seeing your way
clear to, um...

36:33.278 --> 36:35.454
I think she rang off.

36:37.195 --> 36:39.327
Phew.

36:39.371 --> 36:41.373
Why aren't we moving?

36:46.334 --> 36:47.466
No.

36:47.509 --> 36:49.381
No, no, no.

36:49.424 --> 36:51.296
Oh, yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.

36:51.339 --> 36:53.341
You see, our Phoenix TAC team...

36:53.385 --> 36:55.387
The finest in the world,
might I add...

36:55.430 --> 36:57.258
Stopped your real saviors

36:57.302 --> 36:59.608
long before they ever hit
the ground.

36:59.652 --> 37:02.307
All the fighting, the gunfire.

37:04.134 --> 37:07.137
All right, team. All clear.

37:12.708 --> 37:13.927
Yes, well,

37:13.970 --> 37:16.234
good old Boze here, he staged

37:16.277 --> 37:17.496
that for your benefit

37:17.539 --> 37:19.933
using fake rounds
and blood squibs.

37:20.977 --> 37:22.414
But why?

37:22.457 --> 37:23.457
Why?

37:25.808 --> 37:27.549
That's why.

37:30.596 --> 37:32.032
The number he gave us

37:32.075 --> 37:33.618
links to a modem
on a protected network.

37:33.642 --> 37:36.384
Could it lead to the location
of Codex's new headquarters?

37:36.428 --> 37:38.778
It's buried under a few layers,
so it'll take some time.

37:38.821 --> 37:40.562
But I'll find 'em.

37:45.872 --> 37:47.874
Checkmate.

38:10.723 --> 38:12.899
Give it a rest, Riley.

38:12.942 --> 38:15.945
We got The Merchant, the intel

38:15.989 --> 38:17.599
and a handful
of Codex operatives.

38:17.643 --> 38:19.166
Take the night off.

38:19.209 --> 38:20.602
Oh, this isn't about Codex.

38:20.646 --> 38:22.561
I'm doing something
way more stressful.

38:22.604 --> 38:24.432
Apartment hunting.

38:24.476 --> 38:25.694
You're moving?

38:25.738 --> 38:27.261
You don't like my old room
at Mac's?

38:27.305 --> 38:28.456
Look, I know
that place is haunted,

38:28.480 --> 38:30.090
but that stupid priest
was supposed

38:30.133 --> 38:31.570
to take care of it.

38:31.613 --> 38:33.311
No, I...

38:33.354 --> 38:36.314
I just want to give Mac and
Desi the space they deserve.

38:36.357 --> 38:37.706
That's all.

38:37.750 --> 38:40.753
Is that whatyou're telling yourself?

38:43.408 --> 38:45.366
I don't know what
you're talking about.

38:55.376 --> 38:57.335
Don't make me say it.

38:57.378 --> 38:59.337
I won't.

38:59.380 --> 39:01.556
But...

39:01.600 --> 39:03.993
I'm here if you want to talk.

39:07.214 --> 39:09.477
Good night, Riley.

39:10.478 --> 39:12.480
♪

39:41.553 --> 39:44.338
♪

40:07.187 --> 40:09.189
♪

40:17.502 --> 40:19.547
Earlier...

40:19.591 --> 40:21.201
what you said about
me being free

40:21.244 --> 40:23.464
and saving everyone,
what did you mean?

40:23.508 --> 40:26.859
Look, I'm knackered.

40:26.902 --> 40:28.469
Come and see me tomorrow.

40:28.513 --> 40:31.429
Nobody's coming for you, Clive.

40:31.472 --> 40:32.517
Ever.

40:38.392 --> 40:41.526
You know, you're just as trapped as I am.

40:41.569 --> 40:43.571
You just don't realize it.

40:45.007 --> 40:48.489
By your loyalties.

40:48.533 --> 40:52.667
You think that there'sonly
Phoenix and Codex.

40:52.711 --> 40:54.321
But there isn't.

40:58.543 --> 41:02.242
And what else is there?

41:07.508 --> 41:08.814
You.

41:11.381 --> 41:12.576
Let's forget our littlechess match

41:12.600 --> 41:14.515
for a minute, shall we?

41:14.559 --> 41:16.474
And let's pretend thatl
do actually care about

41:16.517 --> 41:18.780
the billions of innocent
soulson this planet.

41:18.824 --> 41:21.522
Well, they're gonna need
someonethat doesn't take sides.

41:21.566 --> 41:24.699
Someone who makesthe hard choices.

41:26.745 --> 41:28.747
I really believedthat person was you.

41:31.184 --> 41:32.707
But you're not ready.

41:32.751 --> 41:34.622
Is that so?

41:34.666 --> 41:37.146
Well, you know that storyl
told you about your aunt?

41:37.190 --> 41:39.845
Yeah, I made that up.

41:41.847 --> 41:45.546
And the reasonyou fell for it...

41:45.590 --> 41:48.593
is you wantedto believe it so badly.

41:50.682 --> 41:54.468
And it moved you,
and that's why you're weak.

41:54.512 --> 41:57.645
You're pretty soft yourself.

41:57.689 --> 41:59.667
When I fed you that lie
about wanting to join Codex,

41:59.691 --> 42:01.257
you lapped it up.

42:04.130 --> 42:06.567
Of course.

42:06.611 --> 42:09.222
You were lying.

42:09.265 --> 42:11.137
Sure.

42:15.271 --> 42:17.273
I was just like you.

